---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  page="home"
  title="Clueless Creations® — A business that runs businesses."
  description="A portfolio holding company running six businesses through an agent harness. Humans on the board; the harness on the floor."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero" style="position: relative; overflow: hidden; height: 100vh; min-height: 720px;">
    <picture>
      <img
        src="/hero/hero-poster.avif"
        alt=""
        loading="eager"
        fetchpriority="high"
        width="1920"
        height="1080"
        class="video-bg"
      />
    </picture>
    <video
      class="video-bg"
      autoplay
      loop
      muted
      playsinline
      preload="none"
      poster="/hero/hero-poster.avif"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
      <source src="/hero/hero.webm" type="video/webm" />
      <source src="/hero/hero.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>
    <div class="vignette" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="relative" style="z-index:10; display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:space-between; height: calc(100vh - 6rem); min-height: 650px; padding: 6rem 1.5rem 3rem; text-align:center;">
      <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center;">
        <div class="animate-fade-rise eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-3);">
          <span class="status-dot status-live pulse-dot"></span>
          A portfolio of agent-run businesses
        </div>
        <h1 class="hero-h1 animate-fade-rise font-display" style="font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5.5vw, 5.5rem); max-width: 900px; margin: 0; letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 0.95; text-shadow: 0 2px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.6), 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);">
          A business that
          <em class="accent-muted">runs</em>
          other
          <em class="accent-muted">businesses.</em>
        </h1>
      </div>

      <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:flex-start; text-align:left; max-width: 30rem; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p class="animate-fade-rise-delay muted" style="font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.65; margin: 0 0 var(--space-8); text-shadow: 0 1px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);">
          Agents discover, validate, build, launch, and operate a portfolio of products.
          Humans sit above as a board of directors — intervening only when judgment is required.
        </p>
        <div class="animate-fade-rise-delay-2" style="display:flex; gap: var(--space-3); flex-wrap: wrap;">
          <a href="/about" class="liquid-glass interactive rounded-full" style="padding: 1.05rem 2.5rem; font-size: .95rem; text-decoration:none;">
            How the harness works →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE PREMISE -->
  <section class="section-well" style="padding: 8rem 1.5rem; background: hsl(var(--background));">
    <div class="container-wide grid md:grid-cols-12" style="gap: var(--space-12);">
      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <div class="eyebrow">01 — The premise</div>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-8">
        <h2 class="display-lg" style="margin:0 0 var(--space-8);">
          We run businesses with agents,
          <em class="accent-muted">and we sell the tools and lessons that come from doing it.</em>
        </h2>
        <p style="font-size:1.125rem; line-height:1.7; max-width: 48rem;" class="muted">
          Four streams feed each other. Running businesses generates lessons that become content.
          Building skills generates tools that become products. Products generate usage that
          sharpens skills. Every motion is leveraged.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="section-well" style="padding: 8rem 1.5rem; background: hsl(var(--background));">
    <div class="container-wide grid md:grid-cols-12" style="gap: var(--space-12);">
      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <div class="eyebrow">02 — The model</div>
        <h2 class="display-md" style="margin: var(--space-4) 0 0;">
          Board, not management.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-8">
        <p class="muted" style="font-size:1.0625rem; line-height:1.7; max-width: 48rem;">
          The harness runs the businesses. The board views through Notion and reports, intervening only at human gates or when the system itself needs improving. When things fail, we fix the harness — not the business. Every failure makes the factory smarter.
        </p>
        <a href="/about" class="liquid-glass interactive rounded-full" style="display:inline-block; margin-top: var(--space-8); padding:.7rem 1.5rem; font-size:.9rem; text-decoration:none;">
          Read the full operating model →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT CTA -->
  <section class="section-well" style="padding: 10rem 1.5rem; background: hsl(var(--background));">
    <div class="container-wide" style="text-align: center;">
      <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">03 — Reach the board</div>
      <h2 class="display-xl font-display" style="margin: 0 auto var(--space-8); max-width: 18ch;">
        <em class="accent-muted">Operators,</em> investors, <em class="accent-muted">fellow travelers.</em>
      </h2>
      <a href="/contact" class="liquid-glass interactive rounded-full" style="display:inline-block; padding: 1.15rem 3rem; font-size: 1rem; text-decoration:none;">
        Get in touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
